# 14. startswith()

## Meaning
Checks whether string starts with given value.

## Problem
Check if string starts with `"py"`.

## Example

```python
s = "python"

print(s.startswith("py"))
```

## Output

```text
True
```

---

# 15. endswith()

## Meaning
Checks whether string ends with given value.

## Problem
Check if string ends with `"on"`.

## Example

```python
s = "python"

print(s.endswith("on"))
```

## Output

```text
True
```

