# 22. center()

## Meaning
Places string at center.

## Example

```python
s = "Python"

print(s.center(20))
```

## Output

```text
       Python
```

---

# 23. format()

## Meaning
Inserts values dynamically into string.

## Example

```python
name = "Ram"

print("Hello {}".format(name))
```

## Output

```text
Hello Ram
```

---

# 24. zfill()

## Meaning
Adds zeros at beginning.

## Example

```python
s = "25"

print(s.zfill(5))
```

## Output

```text
00025
```

---

# 25. removeprefix()

## Meaning
Removes starting prefix.

## Example

```python
s = "unhappy"

print(s.removeprefix("un"))
```

## Output

```text
happy
```

---

# 26. removesuffix()

## Meaning
Removes ending suffix.

## Example

```python
s = "python.py"

print(s.removesuffix(".py"))
```

## Output

```text
python
```

